{"tid":1072495,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗尼：「利物浦捧盃對愛華頓人嚟講係惡夢，唔想再聽佢哋講十年！」","createTime":"2019-03-22T05:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T07:07:10.000Z","uid":33775,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c96a74ec0dea7e09bc8da1c392494a4828040b","tid":1072495,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"今季英超大部分時間都由利物浦佔領先優勢，不過他們在2月份狀態不穩，令到曼城有機可乘，奪冠路途再起波瀾。前曼聯及愛華頓球員朗尼(Wayne Rooney)接受訪問時就坦言寧願曼城奪冠，因為利物浦奪冠對每一個愛華頓人都是一場惡夢。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼出身於愛華頓青訓，更在愛華頓成名，雖然他職業生涯大部分時間為曼聯披甲，但他從未忘本，或應該說他一直都忠於母會，最愛的依然是愛華頓，他在2017-18英超球季返回愛華頓，之後他便離開英格蘭球壇轉戰美職至今。<br />\n<br />\n早前朗尼被問到關於現時英超奪冠情況的問題，他指：「我希望曼城能夠奪得冠軍，如果利物浦捧起冠軍的話，對每一個愛華頓人都是惡夢。我仍記得在2005年利物浦奪得歐聯之後，利物浦球迷至今依然掛在口邊，如果他們奪得英超的話將會再講十幾年。」<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I hope Man City get over the line before Liverpool,&rdquo; he told the Drivetime show.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I couldn&rsquo;t bear to see them win it, it would be a nightmare for any Evertonian.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I remember in 2005 they won the Champions League and they&rsquo;re still talking about it now so it would be another 10 or 15 years of that!&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e83e997b2dbc27da627c6c3573522f78bf4d8ea0","tid":1072495,"uid":52881,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:08:26.000Z","msg":"迪路菲奧！"},{"pid":"a20332dbdcb87d2384a980e0bacb9267d302e6e3","tid":1072495,"uid":72321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"G chi 月巴"},{"pid":"704e5722e37a1430ac2a9d7124690d756e251a35","tid":1072495,"uid":52705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:08:46.000Z","msg":"郎尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d930281f9bd3a4e529419bacd567f298e13883","tid":1072495,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:10:12